I have sent (?) people nobly into the fields, and established holy shrines (?) in the desert. I have built the city itself for a long future in the whole world.

@(A.224 = 224-235) The foreign lands gaze at me, @wRN{Išme-@wDN{Dagan}}, as if at their father who engendered them. When like @wDN{Utu} I decide a just verdict, the people bring their prayers to the holy shrines (?). As I establish and realise my powerful statements, advise the people and strengthen the palace, who is to challenge my powerful statements? …… the foreign lands, their people ……. I snatch men from the jaws of destruction.
